x4freetext: Cyclotron C-200P
A self-supporting 500 micro-g/cm2 foil of carbon with
90% enriched 13C was used as a target.
Two dE-E telescope were used.
dE detectors: Si detectors with thickness 67 micro-m
and 20 micro-m. E detectors:  two silicon
detectors with thickness about 1 mm.
The beam energy spread on the target was about 0.5%
Corrected for background.
Errors include both the statistical errors and
uncertainties from the spectrum fitting procedure.
Data were received from A.T.Rudchik
UKRNDC
OG. REFERENCE: J,YFE,11,(3),251,2010
and #NSR: 2010RU13 were added.
